name: Nifty Royale X Based Fish Mafia The Battle of Coraleone

metadata.description: A bloody war between the mafia and the agents has erupted outside the infamous Coraleone restaurant.
metadata.name: The Battle of Coraleone

attributes.value: Callaby is a British artist currently living in the small country of Montenegro. His work often features anthropomorphic characters painted in his unique, illustrative style. After taking what was meant to be a temporary break from painting canvases last year, he submerged himself in creating the Based Fish Mafia world and hasn't left since.
